==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Roquefort
<hw>Roque`fort"</hw>
}</mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A highly flavored blue-molded
cheese, made at <etsep>Roquefort</etsep>, department of Aveyron, France.
It is made from milk of ewes, sometimes with cow's milk added, and is
cured in caves. Improperly, a cheese made in imitation of it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Roquelaure</ent>⟦br⟧
